---
title: Immersion Heater Decision Logic (coordinator + switch.py)
---
flowchart TD
    START([Coordinator update\nevery 30 s]) --> READ[Read real switch state\ncurrent_on]

    READ --> RUNTO{_immersion_manual\n_run_to_target?}

    RUNTO -- Yes --> TEMPSENS{Temperature\nsensor available?}
    TEMPSENS -- Yes --> ATTARGET{immersion_temp\n≥ target_temp?}
    ATTARGET -- Yes --> RELEASE[Release override → auto\nLog: target reached]
    ATTARGET -- No --> KEEPON[Keep override ON\nReason: 'Manual — running to Xºc']
    TEMPSENS -- No --> KEEPON

    RELEASE --> AUTOPATH
    KEEPON --> CHECKEXT

    RUNTO -- No --> AUTOPATH

    AUTOPATH[Compute should_be_on\nfrom auto-divert logic] --> CHECKEXT

    subgraph AUTO [Auto-divert logic — rules.py]
        AUTOPATH --> LEGIONELLA{Temp below\nmin_temp?}
        LEGIONELLA -- Yes → force on --> OVRIDE[override = True]
        LEGIONELLA -- No --> TARGTEMP{Temp ≥\ntarget_temp?}
        TARGTEMP -- Yes → force off --> OVRIDE2[should_be_on = False]
        TARGTEMP -- No --> BATT{Battery SoC\n< threshold?}
        BATT -- Yes → no divert --> OVRIDE2
        BATT -- No --> SURPLUS{Net solar surplus\n≥ min_surplus\nOR clipping?}
        SURPLUS -- No --> OVRIDE2
        SURPLUS -- Yes --> HYST{Currently OFF AND\ntemp ≥ target − hysteresis?}
        HYST -- Yes → wait to cool --> OVRIDE2
        HYST -- No --> OVRIDE3[should_be_on = True]
    end

    CHECKEXT{External change?\ncurrent_on ≠ last_write\nAND not within cooldown} -- Yes, turned ON --> EXTRON[Activate run-to-target\nClear cooldown\nRecord write]
    CHECKEXT -- Yes, turned OFF --> EXTROFF[Clear run-to-target\nCooldown 10 min\nRelease to auto]
    EXTRON --> DONE([Return])
    EXTROFF --> DONE

    CHECKEXT -- No change detected --> DIFFER{should_be_on\n≠ current_on?}
    DIFFER -- No --> DONE

    DIFFER -- Yes --> OVERTEMP{Water ≥ target\nAND turning off?}
    OVERTEMP -- Yes → bypass cooldown --> WRITE
    OVERTEMP -- No --> COOL{Within\n10-min cooldown?}
    COOL -- Yes → skip --> LOG[Log: cooldown active]
    LOG --> DONE
    COOL -- No --> WRITE[Write turn_on / turn_off\nto real switch entity\nSet 10-min cooldown\nRecord write]
    WRITE --> DONE

    subgraph MANUAL [Manual triggers — bypass cooldown]
        M1([Managed switch ON]) --> MAN1[override = True\nrun-to-target = True\nClear cooldown\nRecord write = True]
        M2([Managed switch OFF]) --> MAN2[override = None\nrun-to-target = False\nCooldown 10 min\nRecord write = False]
        M3([AutoImmersion\nmaster OFF]) --> MAN3[override = False\nPermanently off]
    end
